title: updates to node relationships and non-text qualities do
pid: 25caf264-cda4-4005-8e4a-e571f42befeb
body: |2-
  Each of either kind is an MSV field in the NodeSave type. 
  Each ViewNode type has a program it executes to generate SaveNodes.
  Then they are merged.
  (The program can be mere verification that a
  relative of a certain kind exists to handle it.)
